title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“Library prefers 'indented' children.” [Caption on library bookmarks promoting “Ident-a-Kid” program. From The Columbus Dispatch, 29 August 1984. Submitted by Dorothy Branson, Columbus, Ohio.]
